Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,BATTLE OF TRUE DRAGONS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?! What are they doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it look like?\NThey're fighting a ferocious battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Dai and Hadorra's clashes\Nare causing this gust of heat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just a gust.\NIt's highly concentrated energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They're completely in their own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We escaped here before we got burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?\NHow does this sort of thing even happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A Battle of True Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh?\N-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is truly the Underworld's infamous\NBattle of True Dragons recreated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds quite interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In the distant past...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:03:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the two most powerful\NDragons in the Underworld...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}finally decided to determine\Nwho was stronger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Veruza, the Abyss Dragon...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and Vorikus, the Lightning Dragon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Evenly matched, the clash\Nbetween the two was truly savage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their Auras and flame breath\Nand Magic Power collided,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the super-heated ground\Nwas laid waste.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their battle created\Na field so tempestuous{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it drained the life\Nof any who stood in it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those who approached were incinerated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the end, this ultimate duel\Nof pure power{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was won by Veruza.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:04:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he became the Abyss Dragon King.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since then, this battle is called\Nthe Battle of True Dragons,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and is revered as\Nthe most intense duel in history.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay close attention, Kilban.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't something one sees every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Only when both sides\Nare extremely powerful and evenly matched
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,does such a thing ever happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that those two\Nwould show me such a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both fighting\Nwith all their might.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That energy must be spilling over,\Ncreating that field around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so calm?!\NDai's like that and you're not helping?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see,\Nno one can approach those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:05:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost as though their will\Nis keeping everyone at bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why isn't Dai using his sword?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra isn't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since that heat field appeared,\Nthey've been fighting hand-to-hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they both know\Nthat drawing their weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,will signify the end of their duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not waiting!\NMy Medoroa can blow away any heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hit Hadorra with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:05:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Popp. This is their duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time for platitudes! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just standing there\Nis draining their stamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai may be a Dragon Knight, but between\Nlittle Dai and that huge Hadorra,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it's obvious who has more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if anyone says it's unfair!\NI'm helping Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you too, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai wants this duel.\NThat why we shouldn't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He should just ignore Hadorra's condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't his inability to\Nwhat makes Dai our Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,About the power of Dai's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was Courage,\Nbut Courage is the power of your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, what's his power?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps Dai's power\Nis that naivety you mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,His kindness and innocence...\NThat clarity of heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. His pure heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai was raised on Dermline Island,\Nan island of monsters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So he doesn't discriminate\Nor hold any preconceptions of anyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It allows him to treat everyone\Nequally and naturally.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that his greatest trait?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what allowed us\Nto all become friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It allowed Hyunckel and Crocodine\Nto become our allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason we're all here now\Nis thanks to the power of Dai's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So if Dai sensed anything within Hadorra\Nthat made him accept this duel,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:08:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's our duty to respect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,At least that's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't beat him like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... I have to use\Nmy strongest attack against him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,His sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever you're about to do something\Nunbelievable, you make that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's become my favorite face of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beginning. The final clash.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The next attack will decide this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make outlandish predictions!\NHow can you tell that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I think that field...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of that battlefield\Nsides with the victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That super-heated field\Nthat surrounds them
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is maintained because\Ntheir energy is balanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That keeps it at bay and makes it grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, when that balance is tipped...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,all of that energy flows\Nto the weaker side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The weaker side...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:10:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the most dangerous part\Nof the Battle of True Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When the deciding blow is struck,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,all that accumulated energy\Nflows to the side that is struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The loser faces certain death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How scary.\NI'd never have a duel like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary, scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But, in this case,\NDai's disadvantage grows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra's finishing attack\Nwill be his Ultra Combustion Slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But as for Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,his greatest attack is his Aban Strash\Nused with his Dragonic Aura or a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If Raiden is his strongest spell,\Nthen his Magic Sword is nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Between Aban Strash and Ultra\NCombustion Slash, the outcome is obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not something he'd overlook.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So what will he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban Strash...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:28.37,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}TIGER SHATTER FIST{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:33.58,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}ABAN STRASH{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban Strash... So that's your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The attack took my life once,\Nand even after Aban's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.65,0:11:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it was passed on to his successors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, it's the perfect attack\Nto end this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't win with an Aban Strash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you lose, this battlefield...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! All of this heat will flow\Nto whoever loses this clash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you already realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But I, no, Aban Strash won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I developed this\Nto fight Dark King Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a new Aban Strash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A new Strash?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be the new attack\NDai developed in his training!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to save this\Nuntil the fight with Ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But that'll be meaningless if I lose here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to use it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not one to try to\Nbluff your way through a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting! Then show me\Nthis new Aban Strash of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's just some silly attack\Nthen my mighty strike will shatter it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Get farther away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!\NWe can't leave at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then at least get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes, Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His stance is the same.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's slightly deeper than usual.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Aban Strash Arrow!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's his new Strash?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a normal Strash!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?! What makes this an arrow?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:14:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's merely a breeze compared to\Nmy Ultra Combustion Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll blow it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.45,0:14:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Aban Strash Break!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's catching up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...with the first Strash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Aban Strash...{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Cross!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Dai!\NDai used his new super attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Battle of True Dragons\Nhas been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He won! Dai won!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see that?!\NThat unbelievably powerful new Strash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the new super attack\Nthat Dai created.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Aban Strash... Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Aban Strash has the Arrow Type\Nwhere you launch Aura,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Break Type where you\Ncharge the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But to combine the two...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Combine the two?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Hyunckel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean he catches up to his Arrow Type\Nwith his Break Type,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and detonates both Strashes simultaneously\Nat the moment of impact.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The upward impact of the Arrow Type\Nand the downward impact of the Break Type{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}cross at the enemy's chest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:16:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The overlapping force is probably\Nover five times that of a normal Strash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Over five times?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But to time the impact\Nof the two attacks perfectly
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,requires unbelievable instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,To predict an enemy's movements\Nand time two attacks is beyond even me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a super attack only Dai can pull off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A super attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.13,0:16:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks like\NDai has spent all his Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra's finished, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That tremendous energy\Nthat surrounded them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that it's gone means\Nit hit him with that Strash Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! He's still...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's his will!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable! Hadorra shouldn't have\Na shred of Aura left!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All of their Aura\Nwere blown away in that clash!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does he get that strength?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A Life Blade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra is converting his own life\Nand making it his sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he knows what it'll cost him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They were all defeated... My Royal Guard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hym... Albinass... Sigma...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've all done well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will join you all soon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In retrospect, the Six Legion Commanders\Nof the Dark Army were all mighty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But they couldn't defeat\NDai and his friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's because, as their commander, I had\Nnothing but greed and self-preservation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The fact that you all came together\Nand risked your lives for me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}feels like the greatest proof\Nthat I was able to reach great heights.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the very end, I was blessed\Nby my servants.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall answer your loyalty\Nwith this strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no! It feels like Hadorra's will\Nis totally overpowering Dai's!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:19:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Getting hit by that super attack\Nwasn't enough to defeat him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can tell that this strike contains\Nthe will of the Royal Guard, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we get hit, it'll all be over!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive anyone\Nwho helps me here! Not even you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,For just this battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to let me fight alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have that sort of strength left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That last attack used up all of your Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra is using the remaining\Nbit of his life for one final attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It contains his will and\Nthe unfulfilled wishes of the Royal Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't win with any normal attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And with all of your Aura spent,\Nyou can't use Strash Cross either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!\NJust leave the rest to us, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,one attack I want to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Hadorra's not the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,carrying the wishes\Nof his friends as he fights!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's always with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Master and Grampa and Dad, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to prove their belief in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't lose to Hadorra here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really am just a coward.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.30,0:21:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why couldn't I believe\Nin someone this strong?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You've spoken well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But what can you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You barely have any Aura left!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Raiden!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:12.14,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:18.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:23.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:29.87,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:35.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:41.84,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:47.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:53.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:59.27,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:01.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:05.19,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:10.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:16.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:22.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:25.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:30.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai won the Battle of True Dragons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Hadorra rose again\Nthrough sheer force of will.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.69,0:23:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the wishes of the fallen Royal Guard\NHadorra readies a mighty attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Against him, Dai readies his Magic Sword.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With his Aura spent,\Ncan Dai defeat Hadorra?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.29,0:23:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Last Attack"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.04,0:24:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.21,0:24:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,
